Hi Scott,

You too may already have the notification email below, but just to confirm =
I have just submitted a slightly shorter version of our article to the Indu=
strial Relations Journal. This is a CABS 3 journal - ranked as internationa=
lly excellent. This is not quite the level of Work Employment and Society b=
ut less rework was required and this would still be a thoroughly respectabl=
e outlet. I did also look at the Social Indicators Research journal, howeve=
r this does not currently feature on the CABS list at all, so I think we wo=
uld be downgrading our contribution unnecessarily at this stage. I am hopef=
ul that we are a good enough fit for the  IRJ to get beyond the desk review=
 this time.

Hope you have a great festive break - and that we have some good news to co=
me back to in the New Year.

Happy holidays!

Best wishes
Caroline




